outputs.output_descr:
The overall objective of this project is to strengthen the fundamentals on energy cooperation for Northeast Asia and the Tumen Region. The key outputs are: 
1) Identifying Cooperation Opportunities and Providing Policy Recommendations Recommendations
2) Building-up a Capacity of the Governments in Northeast Asia for Energy Cooperation

project_descr: Baseline Study and Capacity Building for Energy Cooperation in Northeast Asia
project_title: Energy baseline study in Northeast Asia
